

| ![][image1] | “EastOpening” First room of East. NPC drifter near right side. 2 gearbits. |
| :---- | :---- |
| ![][image2] | “SwordBridge” Titan Hand, Titan Sword Unskippable cutscene introduces shuriken frogs. 1 gearbit can only be reached from ThePlaza. 2 gearbits, 1 health pack. |
| ![][image3] | “FlameElevatorEnter” Elevator room, spawnwarp saves 2 seconds in low%. |
| ![][image4] | “WaterTunnelLAB” Cough Module Unskippable cough cutscene. First and fastest module in East. 1 module. |
| ![][image5] | “ThePlaza” Hub room, Warp pad, Waypoint room East main hub. 1 gearbit is only reachable from the back of EastLoop, a monolith and 1 gearbit are only reachable from DocksBridge, the doors leading to BogStreet are only reachable from DeadOtterWalk. 2 gearbits, 1 monolith. |
| ![][image6] | “NPCDrugDen” Church, Pews, Otters NPCs taking shelter here. |
| ![][image7] | “TowerEast” Cough Bridge Down the stairs from ThePlaza. Unskippable cough cutscene. 1 health pack. |
| ![][image8] | “MegaHugeLAB” Arena with melties unlocks the top half of the room with a module and the bottom half of the room with several gearbits. 5 gearbits, 10 health packs, 1 module. |
| ![][image9] | “MeltyMashArena” 1 Key Door 2 gearbits, 2 health packs. |
| ![][image10] | “FlamePitLAB” Flame Room, Flamethrower Module Level files claim that there are 2 health kits but one of them is out of bounds and unreachable (no floor there). Orange outfit. 2 gearbits, 1 outfit, 1 module, 1 health pack. |
| ![][image11] | “FlameElevatorExit” |
| ![][image12] | “DeadOtterWalk” Jackal room, Anubis room, Guardian room Unskippable Anubis and pink drifter cutscenes. Dash challenge reachable with laser, zaliska, or impact rifle. 2 gearbits, 1 key, 1 monolith. |
| ![][image13] | “BogStreet” 3 Module Door Left side with the elevator is accessed via the green door, right side via the 3 module door. Unskippable cutscene introduces jar frogs. 2 gearbits. |
| ![][image14]![][image15]![][image16] | “BigBogLab” 3 Key Door Lower and upper halves of this room are disjoint. Falling platforms in the upper half can spawnwarp the drifter to the lower half, so be extra careful not to fall on them. 6 gearbits, 1 key, 7 health packs, 1 module. |
| ![][image17] | “BogTempleCamp” Boss Door, Drawbridge Arena, Shotgun Module Arena must be cleared once to gain access to upper BigBogLab and then a second time to access the boss door. The module after the region boss is in the upper left of this room. 3 gearbits, 1 monolith, 1 module, 6 health packs. |
| ![][image18] | “FrogBoss” Cleaner, The Emperor, Shotgun, Blunderbuss Disjoint room \- right side is the East Boss arena, left side contains the shotgun. 3 gearbits, 1 weapon (shotgun). |
| ![][image19] | “TempleIshVault” East Pillar Room, East Pylon Room. 1 health pack, 1 pylon. |
| ![][image20] | “PlazaAcessLab” White Outfit, White Cloak, 8 Key Door Room down the elevator from BogStreet. 8 key door contains the white outfit. 3 gearbits, 1 outfit, 1 key, 3 health packs. |
| ![][image21]![][image22] | “DocksLab” Mycelium Arena 1 of the shuriken frogs in this arena is not required. Save point near the elevator to DocksCampfire. 2 gearbits, 3 health packs, 1 module. |
| ![][image23] | “DocksCampfire” The topmost room of East. 1 gearbit, 1 key, 1 health pack. |
| ![][image24] | “Docksbridge” Drowned Titan Room, Sunken Titan Room There is a save point on the stairs just above the bottom arena. That arena does not require any enemies to be killed in order to leave, if you can complete the unlock interaction without getting hit. 2 gearbits, 2 health packs. |
| ![][image25] | “FrogArena” Ballet Module, Autoscroller Arena, Autoscroller Module Falling platforms arena is essentially an autoscroller. Using only melee attacks when possible will minimize lag frames. 2 health packs, 1 module. |
| ![][image26] | “PlazaToLoop” This room is a hallway. |
| ![][image27] | “EastLoop” 8 Module Door, Dash Challenge Room containing the 8 module door. The exit from the 8 module dungeon gives access to a monolith here and a gearbit in ThePlaza. 1 gearbit, 1 monolith, 1 module, 2 health packs. |
| ![][image28] | “LoopLAB” 8 Module Dungeon 3 gearbits, 2 health packs. |
| ![][image29] | “MeltyLeaperArena” 8 Module Arena, Crystal Shotgun, Diamond Shotgun Arena with melties and leapers (and dirks). Save point at entrance. 1 gearbit, 1 weapon (diamond shotgun). |
